{"tid":504862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港茶記算唔算世界上最無得頂既文化？","createTime":"2017-12-20T13:25:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-21T05:49:56.000Z","uid":123264,"like":371,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"ae0d4df85404e9f7ab7d3bcd6271518e0322ecf7","tid":504862,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T13:25:30.000Z","msg":"屌你老母花錢買難受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上菜慢，落單慢，又甩單，甩完單叫你等多半個鍾就算，對唔住都唔駛講，好似欠撚左你咁，催佢又發癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話咩有特色，根本十間有十間都淨係識整例牌菜式，都算，仲要整唔好，一PAT汁兩舊肉，又貴又小，依家菜都唔比你兩條，根本比狗食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食到膠，食到昆蟲，食到屎同佢講又黑你面，錢又照比當無野發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n班慒西仲成日去吹奏間垃圾維記，野又唔好食，又要比人屌，其實話茶記代表左香港文化真係無錯，香港人就係中意比人屌屎忽慒西越比人屌越爽皮，真係無得頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64707af5a326ac3128ba5a3cdd5c6b60db0a43bb","tid":504862,"uid":20449,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T13:28:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"86737a664421a264f33bd40a4141199cf70bc104","tid":504862,"uid":101571,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T13:28:28.000Z","msg":"香港獨有特色 幾好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2941a453efd7e244bb5e8924d388eea2d5963944","tid":504862,"uid":55533,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T13:29:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有人食茶記？</blockquote><br />\n澳牛日日排隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6ce55e632d74e8ccd6ef916bf089a3b59798608","tid":504862,"uid":53672,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T13:31:16.000Z","msg":"唔食茶記咪大家樂，到時執哂又屌"},{"pid":"31d726d3ff80d2a29e051df28ff04131c3a38ec2","tid":504862,"uid":57844,"like":14,"dislike":29,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T13:32:18.000Z","msg":"茶記不知幾正，垃圾樓主想做飲食集團打手"},{