ote><blockquote>唔食茶記咪大家樂，到時執哂又屌</blockquote><br />\n大家樂咪又係狗糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n吉野家先叫正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食過日本吉野家之後，會諗究竟香港果間其實係唔係只係掛個名"},{"pid":"8638520cb956cceab635e4d896358647172a4b86","tid":504862,"uid":96,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T14:11:39.000Z","msg":"之前返工試左附近兩間平時未食過嘅茶記 屌你老母兩間d炸嘢都未熟嘅 食到我一肚氣<br />\n自此決定以後唔會食以前冇幫襯過嘅茶記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a92ff30ed3fadface37d5525c98a351985a1ca0","tid":504862,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T14:11:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港好公平 除非你食高級野 如果唔係度度都係俾屎你食</blockquote><br />\n100蚊以下基本上都係差唔多食物質素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過好似茶記呢d環境差又食物質素差又貴既真係狗都唔屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aeb0cf768d8048570b59cdfbb79448b01313702","tid":504862,"uid":28151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T14:12:58.000Z","msg":"茶記早餐下午茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n午餐晚餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4776eb264d6ebf3005cc4fd3323cdbea3a278cd7","tid":504862,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T14:14:06.000Z","msg":"俾著第二個國家，應該冇人幫襯，因為串過馬撚<br />\n係香港人覺得無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7766f6f3584651020bbc1e65548e88c3e33cf6fd","tid":504862,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T14:17:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>茶記早餐下午茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n午餐晚餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n早餐大家樂有粥有糯米雞，茶記？"},{"pid":"208037e2a3b3390e56dd1d9b39a0e9c8284f5c57","tid":504862,"uid":20867,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T14:28:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>仲有人食茶記？</blockquote><br />\n澳牛日日排隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港人食慣屎無計</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/20/222814_5d23df2adafdb9df4d329e88ca69a377.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F20%2F222814_5d23df2adafdb9df4d329e88ca69a377.jpg&h=37d4b13b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f03241d032b1b935affcb2b2bcdf436e8671add5","tid":504862,"uid":163758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T14:31:39.000Z","msg":"特登開acc黎覆<br />\n係香港食野真係攞交黎嘈<br />\n一係就小9大陸人亂9咁做野, 一係就同香港伙記亙小"},{"pid":"76a1b1868f04dbf4d477fb619c0cd6a3aead1821","tid":504862,"uid":40867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T14:35:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老母花錢買難受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上菜慢，落單慢，又甩單，甩完單叫你等多半個鍾就算，對唔住都唔駛講，好似欠撚左你咁，催佢又發癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話咩有特色，根本十間有十間都淨係識整例牌菜式，都算，仲要整唔好，一PAT汁兩舊肉，又貴又小，依家菜都唔比你兩條，根本比狗食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食到膠，食到昆蟲，食到屎同佢講又黑你面，錢又照比當無野發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n班慒西仲成日去吹奏間垃圾維記，野又唔好食，又要比人屌，其實話茶記代表左<span style=\"color: red;\">香港文化</span>真係無錯，香港人<span style=\"color: red;\">就係中意比人屌屎忽慒西越比人屌越爽皮</span>，真係無得頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌你 呢d咪獅子山下體精神lo<br />\n講嘢咁唔小心 小心比情懷撚咬死你"},{"pid":"f602265c99e5c8b4d35d7191fe5bf869f552c23f","tid":504862,"uid":89608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T14:49:09.000Z","msg":"都冇計, 平民食店, 唔係快餐店就係茶記, <br />\n<br />\n快餐店好多野都唔及茶記, 例如炒野, <br />\n<br />\n有時真係局住食, <br />\n<br />\n年紀大都冇可能餐餐麥當勞, <br />\n<br />\n不過好彩, 我平時食開個間茶記, 態度OK, 野食好味, <br />\n<br />\n最緊要杯奶茶都合我口味, 所以我就覺得冇乜問題"},{"pid":"eb15cd875fbd508ab7b11a3709b1e1554c32b3af","tid":504862,"uid":60015,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T15:08:55.000Z","msg":"啱曬香港地班奴隸<br />\n唔撚俾人屌下唔安樂"},{"pid":"9ecb744aaf839607cfcc362ba4bd10fb805e5947","tid":504862,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T15:09:07.000Z","msg":"茶記食碟頭飯，炒嘢，小菜等等，八九成中伏<br />\n<br />\n去茶記多數只會食早餐/常餐/下午茶，但都要識揀，嘔麵/火腿通/西多/三文治/多士，飲杯奶茶，多數起碼入到口"},{"pid":"d6426f6189ceac735ca853916e1252a1cefb3aea","tid":504862,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T15:09:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>仲有人食茶記？</blockquote><br />\n澳牛日日排隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港人食慣屎無計</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/20/222814_5d23df2adafdb9df4d329e88ca69a377.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F20%2F222814_5d23df2adafdb9df4d329e88ca69a377.jpg&h=37d4b13b&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係唔明點解咁撚普通嘅嘢都吹奏 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"736132580094ab541ece77fc708e7b058d607483","tid":504862,"uid":516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T15:10:17.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"28ccd1a90171c88972fd64c0bb0d46b1cbe1f36a","tid":504862,"uid":59522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T15:11:55.000Z","msg":"維記都屌？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你有啊姐咁好記性先屌啦"},{"pid":"8421980af083f31eb756fd0a22bebbce9c152734","tid":504862,"u